reviewText: I got this for my brother who is a huge drag racing fan and he loved it

a very good dvd.  if you like don garlits or drag racing you will enjoy this film. I have been a drag racing fan  from about age 10  back in 1969 .  The film shows drag racing in the 1960s, 1970s and 80 and 90s  It shows a lot of garlits wins you saw on tv. It is well worth the 10 dollars.
Great video about the Greatest Drag Racer of all time!
